file.name: openapi30.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: test request body parameters
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /book:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Book'
        required: true
      responses:
        '201':
          description: created book
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Book'

components:
  schemas:
    Book:
      type: object
      properties:
        isbn:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string
